content: अशिष्ट {%<ab>a.</ab>%} {@--1@} Ill-bred, ill-behaved, rude. {@--2@} Unrefined, barbarous, not respectable, unworthy; °आलापेन <ls>Pt. 4.</ls> {@--3@} Atheistical, profane. {@--4@} Not sanctioned by any recognized authority. {@--5@} Not prescribed in any work of authority; °ता, °त्त्वं rudeness.
